# Profile Image

This directory should contain your profile/about page photo.

## Required Image:
- **profile.jpg** - Your photographer portrait
  - Recommended dimensions: 800x800px or higher (1:1 square aspect ratio)
  - Format: JPG (optimized for web, under 200KB recommended)
  - Description: Professional headshot or portrait of yourself
  - Style: Will be displayed with grayscale filter on the About page

## How to Add:
1. Select a professional photo of yourself
2. Rename it to `profile.jpg`
3. Place it in `/public/photos/about/profile.jpg`
4. The About page will automatically display it in grayscale

This image appears on the left side of the About page in a two-column layout.
